 vor allem in Betracht.</p><closer>Mit verbindlichen Grüssen<lb/>Ihr ergebener<lb/><signed><handShift/>ArthSchnitzler</signed></closer><postscript><p><handShift medium="typewriter"/>Herrn Robert Adam, <rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs>.</p></postscript></div></body><back><listPerson><person xml:id="pmb2121">
